        <item>
            <title>日本名古屋鐵道試行「空手觀光」   去機場前託運行李 + GPS 標籤可追蹤</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/japan-travel-luggage/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japan-travel-luggage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/japan-travel-luggage/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 08:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220210</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p class="-ml-3 md:ml-0"><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">據日媒報道，</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">日本名古屋鐵道公司、名古屋車站及中部國際機場將在</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">中部國際機場和北海道新千歲機場的部分航班測試</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">「空手觀光」，讓遊客可在去機場前預先報到後託運行李。<br /></span></p><p class="-ml-3 md:ml-0"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220318" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/047screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/047screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/047screenshot.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="-ml-3 md:ml-0"><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">據富士新聞網報道，現時旅客</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">去機場前可以在名古屋車站寄存行李，</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">預先報到後</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">登記託運行李</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">就能直接將行李</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">送上預定航班。這項措施能夠節省旅客</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">在機場排隊報到的時間。</span>旅客於名古屋車站寄存行李後，工作人員會將託運行李送上專車，寄送往日本中部國際機場。工作人員會在行李上貼 GPS 標籤，讓旅客追蹤行李位置。</p><p>日本希望「空手觀光」計畫可縮短旅客於機場等待的時間，從而減低航空公司壓力，以及紓緩排隊人潮。據悉日本目標是在 2025 年大阪關西世博前正式落實上述措施。</p><p><div class="video-container"><iframe title="回送列車で運び搭乗機まで…『手ぶら旅行』の実証実験，駅で荷物預けて手ぶらで空港へ 名鉄等が実用化目指す" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IpNl-DB2_Z4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.fnn.jp/articles/-/657472">FNN</a>、<a href="https://udn.com/news/story/6812/7754547">聯合新聞網</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/japan-travel-luggage/life-tech/travel/">日本名古屋鐵道試行「空手觀光」   去機場前託運行李 + GPS 標籤可追蹤</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
