        <item>
            <title>OpenAI Sora 發佈【有片睇】超強 AI 文字生成影片</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/openai-sora/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=openai-sora</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/openai-sora/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:38:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI sora]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220324</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OpenAI 日前發布了全新影片生成模型 Sora ，讓用家可以用文字生成影片。據《Mashable》報道，Sora 可以生成 1 分鐘的影片，而且這些影片非常逼真，看起來就如真實拍攝般樣。網民對 Sora 態度兩極，部分網民表示有興趣試玩 Sora ，另外有網民則表示擔心影片製作行業將會式微。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Introducing Sora, our text-to-video model.</p><p>Sora can create videos of up to 60 seconds featuring highly detailed scenes, complex camera motion, and multiple characters with vibrant emotions.                                 <a href="https://t.co/7j2JN27M3W">https://t.co/7j2JN27M3W</a></p><p>Prompt: 「Beautiful, snowy… <a href="https://t.co/ruTEWn87vf">pic.twitter.com/ruTEWn87vf</a></p><p>&mdash; OpenAI (@OpenAI) <a href="https://twitter.com/OpenAI/status/1758192957386342435?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><div class="container"><div class="grid-layout"><div class="grid-col-span-6 md:grid-col-start-2 lg:grid-col-start-4"><div class="ui-richtext f-subhead-1-5"><p>Sora 能夠生成有多個人物的影片。除此之外，用家亦可以設定影片人物的動作，以及影片背景的細節。Sora 模型可以理解使用者的 Prompt 要求之餘，更可按照現實世界的物理生成影片。</p></div><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zxx" dir="ltr"><a href="https://t.co/rmk9zI0oqO">https://t.co/rmk9zI0oqO</a><a href="https://t.co/WanFKOzdIw">pic.twitter.com/WanFKOzdIw</a></p><p>&mdash; Sam Altman (@sama) <a href="https://twitter.com/sama/status/1758219575882301608?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></div></div></div><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220326" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708063122-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708063122-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708063122.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Prompt: Tour of an art gallery with many beautiful works of art in different styles</p><p>OpenAI 表示，Sora 暫時仍然有弱點，有時可能無法理解邏輯關係，例如生成一個人食餅乾的片段時，餅乾或不會出現咬痕。Sora 有時亦會混淆用家 Prompt 的空間細節，例如會左右不分，以及暫時無法遵從用家 Prompt 要求的運鏡。</p><div class="mt-spacing-7 overflow-hidden"><div class=""><div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-[1.75em]"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220327" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240216140545-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240216140545-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240216140545.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span class="line-clamp-2 max-w-prose">▲Prompt: Step-printing scene of a person running, cinematic film shot in 35mm.</span></div></div></div><div></div><div class="mt-spacing-7 overflow-hidden"><div class=""><div></div></div></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://openai.com/sora">OpenAI</a>、<a href="https://mashable.com/article/how-to-try-sora-openai-video-generator">mashable</a><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/19/openai-gpt-store-2/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】GPT Store 正式開放 ChatGPT AI 女朋友 + 一張相幫你諗食譜</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/28/gpt4all-no-need-internect-connection/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">GPT4All 不需上網可用 AI【教學】離線安裝 + 免 VPN 實試</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/22/chatgpt-with-voice/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】ChatGPT 語音對話，聽得明廣東話 + 直接語音回答</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/openai-sora/ai/">OpenAI Sora 發佈【有片睇】超強 AI 文字生成影片</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/openai-sora/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
